hopobject.body: I'd like to transfer some money to this account golden root complex blue capsule This isn't about money, or government control or any other political agenda, this is about human lives. American lives. We lost a few thousand Americans in 9-11 and the country was, and still is outraged that we couldn't stop it. We are spending hundreds of billions every year in an effort to prevent another similar occurrence. But Mr. Cruz, you and others will allow about 7 times as many Americans to die every year and not give it a second thought.
